-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/T%C3%A1ng-hoa-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-gA5JJaf5Xy6SshvZx4FFWg">Táng hoa từ - 葬花詞</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/Thanh-H%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng-k%C3%BD/poem-4T3tCDz0kElUt1cfxT71ww">Thanh Hư động ký - 清虛洞記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93ng-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-C%C3%A1t/Thi%C3%AAn-S%C6%A1n-ca/poem-MNQg-4L4zw2Dd1HbLOUHyA">Thiên Sơn ca - 天山歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93ng-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-C%C3%A1t/author-rT4JE0Ax7ttoqnPYUvKzPg">Hồng Lượng Cát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/Thi%E1%BA%BFu-ni%C3%AAn-du/poem-HrmL-4n8pCY_yg_e6FtmYQ">Thiếu niên du - 少年遊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br></div>	</div>
